data.description: Come check out this well maintained and updated 3 bed, 1 bath home. Property offers main floor laundry, walk in closets, larger living room with hardwood floors. Some updates include, a new walk-in shower in the bathroom, newer paint throughout the home, newer carpet in the bedrooms. Property has enough space for you to build a 2+ car garage or shop! Home has an 140sqft deck on the back side. Very close to parks, lakes, trails and other recreation areas. Wonderful and safe neighborhood offering many restaurants and a local grocery store. Get in today to see this place!
